# API base URL used by the frontend at build/runtime.
# In development Vite will proxy `/api` to this value if set.
# In production the frontend will use this full URL for API calls.
# If `VITE_API_URL` is NOT set at build time, the frontend will default to:
# https://traveling-video-creator-production.up.railway.app
# To override, set `VITE_API_URL` to your backend URL.
VITE_API_URL=
